 Asian capitals by region|state=collapsed}}\n{{World's most populated urban areas}}\n}}\n{{Subject bar |book= |portal2=Geography |portal3=Bangladesh |portal4=Asia |commons=yes |n=yes |n-search=Category:Dhaka |wikt=yes |b=yes |q=yes |s=yes |v=yes |voy=yes |d=yes |d-search=Q60}}\n{{Featured article}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Dhaka| ]]\n[[Category:History of Bengal]]\n[[Category:Bengal]]\n[[Category:Capitals in Asia]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Dhaka Division]]\n[[Category:South Asia]]\n[[Category:Cities in Bangladesh]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:17th-century BC establishments]]\n[[Category:Capitals of Bengal]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|the capital city|the division|Dhaka division|the district|Dhaka district|other uses|Dhaka (disambiguation)}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{use Bangladeshi English|date=September 2019}}\n{{short description|Capital of Bangladesh}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- Basic info -------------->| name                            = Dhaka\n| native_name                     = {{lang|bn|\u09a2\u09be\u0995\u09be}}\n| other_name                      = Dacca\n| settlement_type                 = [[Capital city]]\n| image_skyline                   = {{Photomontage|position=center\t\n| photo1a                         = Dhaka 14th March (32624769393).jpg\n| photo2a                         = National Assembly (25967498804).jpg\t\t\n| photo2b                         = Recreational value of Hatirjheel.jpg\t\t\t\t\n| photo3a                         = Curzon Hall - Northern Facade - University of Dhaka - Dhaka 2015-05-31 1992.JPG\t\t\n| photo3b                         = Diwan-i-Am and Tomb of Pari Bibi with Garden - North-western View - Lalbagh Fort Complex - Dhaka 2015-05-31 2715.JPG\t\n| photo4a                         = Uttra,Dhaka \u0989\u09a4\u09cd\u09a4\u09b0\u09be \u09a2\u09be\u0995\u09be.jpg\t\n| spacing                         =  \t\n| color_border                    = white\t\n| color             